                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/16471",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=mbowie",
                        "name": "mbowie",
                        "displayName": "Mike Bowie",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Interestingly enough, I've been hanging out to post the same issue regarding 'Courier New'.  (COUR.TTF)\n\nAug 28 11:36:34 www3 httpd: PHP Fatal error:  Uncaught exception 'Zend_Pdf_Exception' with message 'Glyph number is out of range: 3' in \/usr\/local\/www\/strongaero.com\/includes\/Zend\/Pdf\/Resource\/Font.php:477\nStack trace:\n#0 \/usr\/local\/www\/strongaero.com\/includes\/Zend\/Pdf\/Resource\/Font\/OpenType.php(147): Zend_Pdf_Resource_Font->widthsForGlyphs(Array)\n#1 \/usr\/local\/www\/strongaero.com\/includes\/Zend\/Pdf\/Resource\/Font\/OpenType\/TrueType.php(53): Zend_Pdf_Resource_Font_OpenType->__construct(Object(Zend_Pdf_FileParser_Font_OpenType_\n(Trace truncated thanks to syslog)\n\nI'll try converting it to pfa and back and see if it helps; sadly I'm not sufficiently familiar with TTF and company to know where to start for a patch.\n\nMuch as I'd love to post a copy of the font, I don't think Microsoft class it as freeware just yet.\n\nCheers,\n\nMike.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=mbowie",
                        "name": "mbowie",
                        "displayName": "Mike Bowie",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-08-28T13:49:21.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-08-28T13:49:21.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/16472",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alexander",
                        "name": "alexander",
                        "displayName": "Alexander Veremyev",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Thanks for the info Mike!\n\nCould you also attach font to the issue (if it's allowed by font license)?\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alexander",
                        "name": "alexander",
                        "displayName": "Alexander Veremyev",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-08-28T14:59:49.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-08-28T14:59:49.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/16473",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=mbowie",
                        "name": "mbowie",
                        "displayName": "Mike Bowie",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Alexander,\n\nIt would seem they are available for download from http:\/\/umn.dl.sourceforge.net\/sourceforge\/corefonts\/courie32.exe  (As I understand it, the license does not allow distribution other than in their original form.)\n\nThe file can be extracted using cabextract on non-Windows platforms.\n\ncour.ttf in that particular package is 2.82, which exhibits the behavior; as does 2.9, which I tried from one of the local Windows XP installations.\n\nHope that helps,\n\nMike.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=mbowie",
                        "name": "mbowie",
                        "displayName": "Mike Bowie",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-08-28T15:55:57.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-08-28T15:55:57.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/17472",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=iezzip",
                        "name": "iezzip",
                        "displayName": "Philip Iezzi",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I'm encountering the same issue with the freeware OCR-B font from http:\/\/ansuz.sooke.bc.ca\/software\/ocrb.php\nAny solution to this problem so far?\nIf not, is there any other freeware OCR font that works with Zend_Pdf_Resource_Font?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=iezzip",
                        "name": "iezzip",
                        "displayName": "Philip Iezzi",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-11-08T12:16:22.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-11-08T12:16:22.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/17820",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alexander",
                        "name": "alexander",
                        "displayName": "Alexander Veremyev",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "There was a problem in glyph width array processing. It may contain less elements than glyphs are presented in the font. \nLast element contains width for the rest of glyphs list.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alexander",
                        "name": "alexander",
                        "displayName": "Alexander Veremyev",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-12-06T18:55:06.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-12-06T18:55:06.000+0000"
                }
            ]
        }
